<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box with Illustration -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
      <div class="dark:bg-white rounded-xl p-1 inline-block">
        <%= image_tag "nvl5_gram/p058/p058_01.jpg", alt: "Illustrazione indefiniti", class: "w-full rounded-lg mb-4" %>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-3">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Gli <strong>indefiniti</strong> indicano in modo non preciso qualcosa o qualcuno oppure una quantità generica.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 ml-6">
          <p><span class="text-red-500">•</span> Gli <strong class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">aggettivi indefiniti</strong> accompagnano il nome → <strong>alcune</strong> regole, <strong>ciascun</strong> visitatore, <strong>qualche</strong> domanda;</p>
          <p><span class="text-blue-500">•</span> I <strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">pronomi indefiniti</strong> sostituiscono il nome → <strong>ognuno</strong> resti..., <strong>qualcuno</strong> ha....</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Attention Box -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
      <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <strong class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 dark:text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300">Attenzione!</strong> Alcuni indefiniti sono <strong class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">solo aggettivi</strong>,
      altri sono <strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">solo pronomi</strong>, altri ancora sono <strong class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">sia aggettivi sia pronomi</strong>. Osserva.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Table of indefinites -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 overflow-x-auto">
    <table class="w-full border-collapse text-sm md:text-base">
      <thead>
        <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-100 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/50">
          <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 dark:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 px-4 py-3 text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">Solo aggettivi indefiniti</th>
          <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 dark:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 px-4 py-3 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold">Solo pronomi indefiniti</th>
          <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 dark:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 px-4 py-3 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 font-bold">Aggettivi e pronomi indefiniti</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 dark:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 px-4 py-6 text-center bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/30 dark:text-white">
            <p class="font-semibold">qualche • ogni</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">qualunque • qualsiasi</p>
          </td>
          <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 dark:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 px-4 py-6 text-center bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-white">
            <p class="font-semibold">uno / una • qualcuno • qualcosa</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">ognuno • nulla</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">niente • chiunque</p>
          </td>
          <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 dark:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 px-4 py-6 text-center bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/30 dark:text-white">
            <p class="font-semibold">alcuno • certo • nessuno • molto</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">poco • parecchio • troppo • tanto</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">altro • ciascuno • tutto • tale</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">altrettanto</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="false">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Clicca sugli aggettivi indefiniti<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-red-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span>
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4 space-y-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Ho invitato <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">molti</span> <u>amici</u> al mio compleanno.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Vado a scuola <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">tutti</span> i <u>giorni</u> con la bicicletta.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Quest'auto dà <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">troppi</span> <u>problemi</u>, dobbiamo sostituirla.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4 space-y-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">Ciascun</span> <u>giocatore</u> deve conoscere le regole.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Ci sarà un'<span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">altra</span> <u>occasione</u> per la tua squadra.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">Nessun</span> <u>essere umano</u> ha mai battuto Alpha Go agli scacchi.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
    Esercizi p. <%= link_to "159", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p159"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %> e <%= link_to "163", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p163"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
